<div style="font-size: inherit;"><h1 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Booking System Feature Specification</h1><h2 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Overview</h2><p style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">The booking system enables pet owners to schedule pet sitting services while giving sitters control over their availability and bookings.</p><h2 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Core Functionality</h2><ol style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li>Scheduling Interface<ul><li>Calendar view showing sitter availability</li><li>Time slot selection in 30-minute increments</li><li>Service duration options (1 hour to multiple days)</li><li>Recurring booking option (weekly/monthly)</li></ul></li><li>Booking Flow<ul><li>Step 1: Select service type (walking, sitting, boarding)</li><li>Step 2: Choose date and time</li><li>Step 3: Review pet sitter details and pricing</li><li>Step 4: Add special instructions</li><li>Step 5: Confirm and pay</li></ul></li><li>Confirmation System<ul><li>Automatic notification to sitter</li><li>1-hour window for sitter to accept/decline</li><li>Instant rebooking suggestions if declined</li><li>Booking confirmation email/SMS</li></ul></li><li>Management Tools<ul><li>Dashboard for viewing upcoming bookings</li><li>Modification/cancellation options</li><li>Automated reminders (24h before service)</li><li>Service completion confirmation</li></ul></li></ol><br></div>
